<chapter xmlns="&xmlns;">
	
	<info>
		<title>Day 1</title>
		<subtitle>Installing and Verifying Rails</subtitle>
	</info>

	<procedure>
		<title>Install Rails</title>
		<step>Go to <ulink>http://www.installrails.com/</ulink> and follow the instructions</step>
		<step>
			<para>Downloaded Rails Installer 3.2.2</para>
			<para>Bundles Ruby 2.2.4p173</para>
			<para>Bundles Rails 4.2.4</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>Once done installing, verify the following:</para>
			<para>
				<sgmltag>$ rails -v</sgmltag>
			</para>
			<para>
				<sgmltag>$ ruby -v</sgmltag>
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>The installer should have added this to <sgmltag>PATH</sgmltag></para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</chapter>